<cb:div>
<pb n="0062a" xml:id="I01.0024.0062a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0062a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 24</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0062a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>仇臣生造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0062a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0062a0101">正光五年歲次甲辰七月己酉朔十五日<note n="0062001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30495"/>＝癸【史】</note><note n="0062001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30495"/>【佛拓】，癸【史】</note><app n="0062001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">癸</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30495"/></rdg></app>亥。
<lb ed="I" n="0062a02" type="honorific"/>雍州北地三原縣仇臣生。值遇上世。信心三寶。
<lb ed="I" n="0062a03" type="honorific"/>造石像一<note n="0062002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30496"/>＝區【史】</note><note n="0062002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30496"/>【佛拓】，區【史】</note><app n="0062002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30496"/></rdg></app>。上為皇帝陛下。州郡令長。七世父
<lb ed="I" n="0062a04" type="honorific"/>母。願上生天上。值遇諸佛。下隧人間。侯王長者
<lb ed="I" n="0062a05" type="honorific"/>之家。現世之報。延年益壽。子孫興隆。<note n="0062003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30355"/>＝所【史】</note><note n="0062003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30355"/>【佛拓】，所【史】</note><app n="0062003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30355"/></rdg></app>願如<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">斯</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0062a06" type="honorific"/>夫信欲稱善者。非至德不顯其功。欲游嵩岳者。
<lb ed="I" n="0062a07" type="honorific"/>非空寂<note n="0062004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30478"/>＝亦【史】</note><note n="0062004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30478"/>【佛拓】，亦【史】</note><app n="0062004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亦</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30478"/></rdg></app>不達其<app type="star" corresp="#0062003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30355"/></rdg></app>。昔太子絕思於龍<note n="0062005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30497"/>＝華【史】</note><note n="0062005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30497"/>【佛拓】，華【史】</note><app n="0062005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">華</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30497"/></rdg></app>。身<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">體</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0062a08" type="honorific"/>如來之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">願</unclear>。月<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">辰</unclear>叩白駒而脩禮。<app type="star" corresp="#0062004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亦</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30478"/></rdg></app>蒙神道之助。
<lb ed="I" n="0062a09" type="honorific"/>是以積善成道。累<note n="0062006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30498"/>＝惡【史】</note><note n="0062006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30498"/>【佛拓】，惡【史】</note><app n="0062006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">惡</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30498"/></rdg></app><note n="0062007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30499"/>＝滅【史】</note><note n="0062007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30499"/>【佛拓】，滅【史】</note><app n="0062007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">滅</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30499"/></rdg></app>身。宜斑經藉。流芳來葉。
<lb ed="I" n="0062a10" type="honorific"/>不敢多進。　　親祖仇收　忘父仇進興
<lb ed="I" n="0062a11" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　　　忘叔仇<note n="0062008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30500"/>＝歸【史】</note><note n="0062008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30500"/>【佛拓】，歸【史】</note><app n="0062008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">歸</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30500"/></rdg></app>興</p>
</cb:div>
